6. Authentication APIs

⸻

AUTH-001 Request OTP

Endpoint

POST /auth/otp/request

Request

{
  "mobile": "9876543210"
}

Validation

Required
10 digits
Indian mobile only

Response

{
  "success": true,
  "otpSent": true,
  "expiryMinutes": 5
}

⸻

AUTH-002 Verify OTP

Endpoint

POST /auth/otp/verify

Request

{
  "mobile": "9876543210",
  "otp": "123456",
  "deviceFingerprint": "encrypted_string"
}

Response

{
  "jwtToken": "",
  "refreshToken": "",
  "deviceApprovalRequired": false,
  "user": {}
}

⸻

AUTH-003 Refresh Token

POST /auth/refresh

⸻

AUTH-004 Logout

POST /auth/logout

